items.title: Labor market growth slows dramatically in August with U.S. adding just 54,000 jobs, ADP says
items.description: U.S. private sector hiring rose less than expected in August, per the ADP.

items.title: Euro zone inflation rises to hotter-than-expected 2.1% in August

items.description: CNBC compared the Honey Deuce's price growth since 2015 against the CPI basket.
